        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This bullet is fashioned from a rubbery substance and stamped with the image of a diminutive ant twitching in surprise. The bullet deals no damage on a successful hit. Instead, the target must attempt a DC 19 Fortitude save.",
